animeDescription: Famous Japanese creators challenge the possibilities ofMarine-chan（the famous character of "Umimonogatari"） Co-Making brand new digital idol "iMarine-chan", original song and music video with Users. We put several meaning into "i" of iMarine, such as infinity, icon, internet, imagination, innovation, ideal and I.(Source: Official YouTube)
